	"strategy": "17.5 Lugia / Archeops keeps the normal Lugia VSTAR shell: establish Lugia V, evolve into Lugia VSTAR, discard Archeops, use Summoning Star, then use Primal Turbo to convert Special Energy into pressure. Nest Ball and Mesagoza are setup tools for Lugia V, Minccino, and only later Wyrdeer V or Regigigas. Wyrdeer V and Regigigas are midgame or late-game attackers after the engine is online; do not let them crowd the opening bench before Lugia VSTAR and Archeops are ready. Prioritize attack-cost completion and prize pressure before terminal attacks, and stop low-value draw churn once a ready attacker and backup plan are established.",
